\c 14
\s Ilizwe leKhanani labiwa ngenkatho
\p
\v 1 Lala \add ngamazwe\add* abantwana bakoIsrayeli abawadla abe yilifa elizweni leKhanani, uEleyazare umpristi loJoshuwa indodana kaNuni lenhloko zaboyise bezizwe zabantwana bakoIsrayeli ababanika wona aba yilifa\x + Nani 34.17,18.\x*,
\v 2 ngenkatho yelifa labo, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi, ngezizwe eziyisificamunwemunye lengxenye yesizwe\x + Nani 26.55. 33.54. 34.13. Hlu. 20.9.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba uMozisi wayesenike ilifa izizwe ezimbili lengxenye yesizwe ngaphetsheya kweJordani; kodwa kumaLevi kanikanga ilifa phakathi kwazo\x + 13.7,8,32,33.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba abantwana bakoJosefa babeyizizwe ezimbili, uManase loEfrayimi\x + Gen. 48.5. 1 Lan. 5.1,2.\x*. Njalo kabawanikanga amaLevi isabelo elizweni, ngaphandle kwemizi yokuhlala, lamadlelo ayo ezifuyo zabo lempahla zabo\x + Gen. 34.23; 36.6.\x*.
\v 5 Njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi, abantwana bakoIsrayeli benza njalo, balaba ilizwe\x + Nani 35.2; 21.2.\x*.
\s UKalebi unikwa iHebroni
\p
\v 6 Khona abantwana bakoJuda basondela kuJoshuwa eGiligali; uKalebi indodana kaJefune umKenizi wasesithi kuye\x + Nani 32.12; Josh. 14.14; 15.17.\x*: Wena uyalazi ilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhuluma kuMozisi\x + Nani 14.30. Dute. 1.36,38.\x* umuntu kaNkulunkulu mayelana lawe lamayelana lami eKadeshi-Bhaneya\x + Dute. 33.1.\x*.
\v 7 Ngangileminyaka engamatshumi amane lapho uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* ingithuma ngisuka eKadeshi-Bhaneya ukuhlola ilizwe. Ngasengibuyisela kuye umbiko njengokusenhliziyweni yami\x + Nani 13.6,26; 14.6.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa abazalwane bami ababenyuke lami\x + Dute. 1.28.\x* benza inhliziyo zabantu zancibilika\x + Dute. 1.28.\x*; kodwa mina ngayilandela ngokupheleleyo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami\x + Nani 14.24. Dute. 1.36.\x*.
\v 9 UMozisi wasefunga mhlalokho esithi: Isibili umhlaba\x + Nani 14.23,24. Dute. 1.36. 1.3.\x* olunyathele kuwo unyawo lwakho uzakuba ngowakho ube yilifa, lebantwaneni bakho kuze kube nininini\x + Nani 13.22.\x*, ngoba uyilandele ngokupheleleyo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami\x + Nani 14.24. Dute. 1.36.\x*.
\v 10 Khathesi-ke khangela, iN\nd kosi\nd* ingilondoloze ngiphila njengokutsho kwayo okwale iminyaka engamatshumi amane lanhlanu, kusukela esikhathini iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakhuluma ngaso lelilizwi kuMozisi, uIsrayeli esahamba enkangala\x + Nani 14.30.\x*. Khathesi-ke khangela, lamuhla ngileminyaka engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lanhlanu\x + Josh. 14.7.\x*.
\v 11 Ngisaqinile lalamuhla njengasosukwini uMozisi angithuma ngalo\x + Dute. 34.7.\x*. Njengamandla ami ngalesosikhathi, asenjalo amandla ami khathesi, awempi lawokuphuma lawokungena\x + Dute. 31.2.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho-ke nginika lintaba iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakhuluma ngayo ngalolosuku, ngoba wena wezwa mhlalokho ukuthi amaAnaki ayekhona lapho lemizi emikhulu ebiyelwe ngemithangala\x + Nani 13.28,33.\x*. Aluba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilami, ngizawaxotsha elifeni, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 13 UJoshuwa wasembusisa\x + 22.6.\x* wanika uKalebi indodana kaJefune iHebroni ibe yilifa\x + 10.36,37. 15.14. Hlu. 1.20. 1 Lan. 6.56.\x*.
\v 14 Ngalokho-ke iHebroni yaba ngekaKalebi indodana kaJefune umKenizi yaba yilifa kuze kube lamuhla, ngoba wayilandela ngokupheleleyo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 14.8,9.\x*.
\v 15 Lebizo leHebroni kuqala laliyiKiriyathi-Arba, owayengumuntu omkhulu phakathi kwamaAnaki\x + 21.11.\x*. Ilizwe laseliphumula empini\x + 11.23.\x*.
